ws in High Point?\",\"answer\":\"High Point enforces a strict leash law. Dogs must be on a leash and under control when off the owner’s property. There are no exceptions for voice control in public parks.\",\"category\":\"legal\"},{\"question\":\"Is High Point University dog-friendly?\",\"answer\":\"The campus is private and generally restricted, but the surrounding greenways and public city parks are very welcoming to pets.\",\"category\":\"facilities\"}],\"supportCard\":{\"kicker\":\"Furniture Shoppers\",\"title\":\"Visiting with a pet?\",\"description\":\"Find dog-friendly hotels and boarding while you shop the Market.\",\"primary\":{\"label\":\"Travel Guide\",\"href\":\"/travel\"},\"secondary\":{\"label\":\"Boarding\",\"href\":\"/boarding\"},\"footnote\":\"Shop 'til you drop (your leash).\"}}]}]}]\n3e:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"className\":\"related-resources-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"section-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Keep exploring\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"More ways to plan\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Browse statewide guides, submit a listing, or connect with our team.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resources-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"resource-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resource-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-globe\"}]}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"California overview\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"See every city we cover plus statewide insights.\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-arrow-up-right\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"resource-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"resource-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-cha